<br>
I had thought that FT was capped at 15, but many casters, including magicians, appear to have FT18.<br>
<br>
My current FT is 16 with mana regen from Shield of Auras adding another 2 mana per tick I believe, but my magelo profile still shows FT15.  I had always thought that FT was capped at 15 until I saw other people's profiles.  Maybe the FT cap is level dependent since I'm still level 63 ?<br>
<br>
Any insight please ?  Is the new cap FT18 or am I confused on the cap issue ?  Are mana regen buffs from the Koadic robe or Shield of Auras (or TPP for that matter) factored into this figure ?<br>
